<item>
            <title>[LU-12634] Support for linux kernel version 5.3</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12634</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Updates for 5.3 kernel&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;bio-&amp;gt;bi_phys_segments is removed&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;force_sig() task parameter is removed&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;lock_manager_operations-&amp;gt;lm_compare_owner is removed&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;struct_user-&amp;gt;uid_keyring and -&amp;gt;session_keyring are removed.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;for_ifa / endfor_ifa replaced with&#160;in_dev_for_each_ifa_rcu&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
